  "texts": [
    "In each session, 15 cases were read in each treatment arm in batches of five cases.",
    "Treatments were randomly ordered.",
    "This resulted in the radiologist reading each patient case under a different treatment condition over the four sessions.",
    "There was a 2-week washout period 15,39,40 between every session to minimize order effects of radiologists reading the same case multiple times.",
    "This design included across-subject and within-subject variations as well as across-case-radiologist and within-case-radiologist variations in treatment conditions."
  ],
